    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个时间线图来展示页面从创建到发布的完整生命周期。核心是三阶段：起草、排期、正式发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "Published"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三阶段结构。起草阶段的关键动作是什么？是创建页面本身，还是内容编辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "Add content blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "创建页面时published_at是nil，这时候属于Groupware_SprintBacklog的草稿池。然后通过content_page_blocks添加内容区块，这两个动作都要放在起草阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at is nil",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "content_page_blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，起草阶段包含创建页面（published_at为空）和添加内容区块。排期阶段呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "排期阶段的核心是设置published_at为当前时间或未来时间，这时候状态变为scheduled。同时可以更新隐私设置、布局和slug，这些会触发updated_at缓存键的更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Set published_at",
        "scheduled",
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys include updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加排期阶段。最后正式发布阶段，判断逻辑是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "Published"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "当published_at小于等于当前时间，状态变为published。可见性取决于policy：公开或已授权用户才能看到。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at <= now",
        "published",
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下完整流程：起草阶段创建页面（published_at为空）并添加内容区块；排期阶段设置发布时间并更新元数据；发布阶段满足时间条件后上线，按权限策略控制可见性。标题定为Page Publish Lifecycle，对吗？",
